Whether you're hitting the court or just hitting the town, this shoe is sure to make a statement.

So don't miss your chance to score this must-have sneaker. Get your pair today!

Whether you're a New Yorker or just a fan of good style, this limited edition shoe is a must-have for your collection.

description: The Converse Vince Staples x Chuck Taylor All Star 70 Ox 'Big Fish Theory' is a shoe that is inspired by the album of the same name by Vince Staples. Part of our collaboration with hip-hop artist Vince Staples, this shoe is based on the merchandise made for his Life Aquatic Tour staff. Inspired by Staples' album of the same name, this shoe features a black canvas upper with white contrast stitching and orange 'SEA' heel branding. Whether you're a fan of Vince Staples or just looking for a unique and stylish sneaker, this is the perfect shoe for you!

title: Converse Dr. Woo x Chuck Taylor All Star 70 Hi 'Black'  160916C
description: Dr. Woo, the tattoo artist to the stars, has teamed up with Converse to create a new take on the classic Chuck Taylor All Star 70 Hi. The black canvas high-top sneaker is inspired by the 1970s original, with a few modern twists. An embroidered ‘Spider and the Fly’ design, inspired by a famous Mary Howitt poem, adorns the side of the shoe. The tongue is made of leather, with a spider web pattern, and the toe cap is printed with a fly. This redesigned classic is sure to turn heads, whether you’re rockin’ it on the street or the dance floor.

title: Converse Chuck 70 Hi 'Chinese New Year'  164472C
description: A celebration of Lunar New Year, the Converse Chuck 70 High 'Chinese New Year' sneaker is a limited edition release of the iconic Chuck Taylor silhouette. Decorated with multicolor and mixed media overlays, inspired by traditional Chinese patchwork called Bai Jia Yi, the upper is juxtaposed with a shiny black patent leather tongue and translucent black midsole. First introduced in 1917, the Chuck Taylor All Star is the most iconic sneaker in history. Its unmistakable ankle patch has been a symbol of self-expression for generations. The Chuck 70 is a faithful reproduction of the 1970s-era All Star, updated with more substantial construction and premium materials like higher-end canvas and cushioned footbeds.
